quran[26{c,v,t}:
92,15,uss mein nahi jhulsAYga magar woh intahi bud- bakht
92,16,jis ne jhtlaya aur mun phera
92,17,aur uss se daur rakha jaayegaa woh nihayat parhaizgaar
92,18,jo pakeeza honay ki khatir apna maal deta hai
92,19,uss par kisi ka koi ahsaan nahi hai jis ka badla ussay dena ho
92,20,woh to sirf apne Rab bartar ki Raza joi ke liye yeh kaam karta hai
92,21,aur zaroor woh ( uss se ) khush hoga
93,1,qasam hai roz roshan ki
93,2,aur raat ki jabkay woh sukoon ke sath taari ho jaye
93,3,( ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ) tumahray Rab ne tum ko hargiz nahi chorra aur nah woh naraaz howa
93,4,aur yaqeenan tumahray liye baad ka daur pehlay daur se behtar hai
93,5,aur anqareeb tumhara Rab tum ko itna day ga ke tum khush ho jao ge
93,6,kya is ne tum ko yateem nahi paaya aur phir thikana faraham kya ?
93,7,aur tumhe nawaqif raah paaya aur phir hadaayat bakhsh
93,8,aur tumhe nadaar paaya aur phir maldaar kar diya
93,9,lehaza yateem par sakhti nah karo
93,10,aur sa-il ko nah jhirko
93,11,aur apne Rab ki Nemat ka izhaar karo
94,1,( ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ) kya hum ne tumhara seenah tumahray liye khol nahi diya ?
94,2,aur tum par se woh bhaari boojh utaar diya
94,3,jo tumhari kamar torrey daal raha tha
94,4,aur tumhari khatir tumahray zikar ka آوازۂ buland kar diya
94,5,pas haqeeqat yeh hai ke tangi ke sath farakhi bhi hai
94,6,be shak tangi ke sath farakhi bhi hai
94,7,lehaza jab tum farigh ho to ibadat ki mushaqqat mein lag jao
94,8,aur apne Rab hi ki taraf Raghib ho
